betterquesting:10.desc:8:
Osiris, is hot, very very hot... but that's not necessarily a downside, according to the bees that live there.
The scorching atmosphere of this planet has been turned into a massive industrial metal-smelting facility, used to produce, armor? For who?
Why are there millions of bees forging armor? And since we are asking questions, why are bees, which are evidently quite powerful and well-organized, engaging in all these sorts of activities to begin with? Why don't they have a unified front? Why are the bees on each planet not working together?
